  "Description": {
    "English": "An <span class=\"name name-special\">extremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Defensive Shielding</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Dramatically improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">ship strength</span> for increased combat endurance.",
