    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船防御护罩</span>的<span class=\"name name-special\">极强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>极大地提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">船体强度</span>来提升战斗时的耐久度。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">太空船防禦防護罩</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">超強大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>大幅提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船強度</span>以便增加戰鬥持久力。"
